trans-unit.source: Represents a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 表示列印系統硬體或軟體元件的 <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> 屬性 (及其值)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> 表示之 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 屬性的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 為指定的屬性初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`拼字應該做為某些特定的名稱完全相同<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>列印系統物件，包括大小寫的屬性。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "HostingPrintQueue", not "PrintQueue" or "Hostingprintqueue".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A>屬性<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>物件必須使用的拼字"HostingPrintQueue 」、 不"PrintQueue"或"Hostingprintqueue"。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> 表示之 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 屬性的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> class that has the specified value for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 初始化指定屬性擁有指定值之 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`拼字應該做為某些特定的名稱完全相同<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>列印系統物件，包括大小寫的屬性。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "HostingPrintQueue", not "PrintQueue" or "Hostingprintqueue".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.HostingPrintQueue%2A>屬性<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>物件必須使用的拼字"HostingPrintQueue 」、 不"PrintQueue"或"Hostingprintqueue"。

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion from a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> (or from a pointer to such a property) to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> value.
trans-unit.target: 提供由 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> (或這類屬性的指標) 至 <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> 值的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> that is converted.
Provides implicit conversion to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> value from a pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: 提供由指標的 <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> 值至 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" /> that is the converted value of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" />.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintQueueProperty" /> 表示的屬性值。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that can be cast to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintQueue" />.
